{"tid":2306063,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有無人覺得限聚令加罰係為打壓絕無僅有的反對空間","createTime":"2020-11-30T07:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T12:59:30.000Z","uid":94771,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"b6deb5b0202bc034e35c9e985a62d6fcf41deeb9","tid":2306063,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"可能好多人都無注意，11月其實好多同路人搞的放映會，講座，悼念<br />\n<br />\n周梓樂一年都好多人無畏惡法，去悼念<br />\n<br />\n其他小型行動就算唔太多人，但至少有人參加下<br />\n<br />\n香港人無想像中真係轉返日常港豬生活，不過大家都沉係底，參加都唔會再高調咁解<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">如果限聚令加罰等同狗罰香港人的力量又大咗，連參加小型行動的代價都會變大</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後請大家繼續記住12港人<br />\nThank You<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKGlobalConnect/status/1333083734816534531?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGlobalConnect%2Fstatus%2F1333083734816534531%3Fs%3D19&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=1e0e0e1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGlobalConnect%2Fstatus%2F1333083734816534531%3Fs%3D19&h=2fd99086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKGlobalConnect/status/1333083734816534531?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"67acd6ba853157a1fed250d06e1aeb808b03930a","tid":2306063,"uid":374518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T07:26:40.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"63a6095e7c81e45cb30ede5e822940fd03f74b57","tid":2306063,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T07:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cb0c6b605f2d616e449d31ef1b51c5616a8340","tid":2306063,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cl